1. On je uspeo da završi školu *uprkos* lošem zdravstvenom stanju. (He managed to finish school despite his poor health.) 
2. Nastavili smo da se smejemo *uprkos* svim neprijatnostima. (We kept laughing despite all the unpleasantness.) 
3. *Uprkos* svim izazovima, nastavio je da se bori za svoje ciljeve. (Despite all the challenges, he kept fighting for his goals.)
4. *Uprkos* njenim protestima, nismo se predomislili. (Despite her protests, we didn't change our minds.) 
5. Nastavili smo da nastavimo putovanje *uprkos* lošem vremenu. (We kept going on the trip despite the bad weather.)